 1- (ạ̹n ạlạ̉sẖbạl ạḥtạjt .. wạ̹n jạʿt ạlạ̉swd
 nfsy bḥbyby ṭạbt .. fyh ạlạ̉frạḥ btswd)2
 ạlqrạr- (frḥk mạly ḍlwʿy .. fy ạlsẖdẗ wfy ạlạ̉zmạt
 ạsẖbʿ rby jwʿy .. ʿwḍ nfsy mạ fạt)2
 2- (ạ̹n ạlḥzn yạ̉tyny .. ạ̉w fy ạlsẖdẗ bkyt
 ạ̉rwḥ lmyn ysẖfyny .. gẖyrk rby mạ lqyt)2
 3- (jlsẗ fy ḥḍrẗ ḥbyby .. kl ạlậlạm btrwḥ
 yạ nạs mạ hw ṭbyby .. sẖạfy kl ạljrwḥ)2
 4- (ạ̹mlạny yạ rb brwḥk .. fạfrḥ byk bạstmrạr
 qds rwḥy bjrwḥk .. ạ̉ḥyạ klhyb mn nạr)2</lyrics>
